  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    UIPreferencesDialogBuilder
    Provides a dialog (a form) containing abstract user interface to be presented to the user to edit UI related preferences.
    UIPreferencesProvidedService
    Provides the service for starting the UI Preferences Editor Dialog.
    UIPreferencesSCallee
    Handles the service call for starting UI Preferences Editor screen.
    UIPreferencesUICaller
    UI Preferences Editor dialog provider.
